title: Infant mortality rate in Greece 2018
summary: Overall Deaths per 1,000 live births has increased over the Year.
Deaths per 1,000 live births is slightly increasing from 2011 to 2015.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum Deaths per 1,000 live births, about 3.8 was reported at Year 2015
The lowest Deaths per 1,000 live births, of value 3.3 was reported at Year 2011
